high_descs: Move to the sink.
Pick up the knife from behind the sink.
Bring the knife to the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the left rear of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife on the stove.
Bring the pan to the left side of the white table.
Put the pan down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking to the stove, then hang a right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the metal butter knife from behind the sink.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the stove.
Place the metal butter knife handle down in the frying pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the frying pan with the metal butter knife in it.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the end of the small white table.
Place the frying pan with a metal butter knife in it onto the white table in front of the stool.
anns.task_desc: Place a frying pan with a metal butter knife in it on a white table.

high_descs: turn and walk over to the kitchen sink
grab a butter knife off of the counter behind the sink
walk over to the kitchen stove
place the knife in the sauce pan on the stove
pick up the sauce pan off of the stove
walk over to the white kitchen table
place the sauce pan on top of the white kitchen table
anns.task_desc: put a sauce pan with a butter knife on it on top of the kitchen table
